  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 10 girls to begin a menstral Pads business</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will help 10 female jobless youths to make reusable sanitary pads for school girls who miss school during their menstrual cycle or completely drop out of school because blood &apos;embarrassed&apos; them in the classroom. They will be making reusable sanitary towels for 700+ females at REF community center and 5,000+ female villagers in the surrounding communities. This beneficiary-centered project will fight menstrual stigma in rural communities and promote menstrual hygiene among women.</narrative>
  </description>
